                    <p>Timeliness is measured as the difference between a project's start date and the date it is submitted to NGO Aid Map.  The visualization below shows the timeliness with which organizations provided information on projects starting in 2014 or later. Projects with earlier start dates are not included because prior to 2014 organizations could only submit data on projects taking place in certain countries or sectors.  NGO Aid Map became global, covering all countries and sectors, in 2014 <a href="//www.ngoaidmap.org/p/history">(more on its history here)</a>.</p>
